The paper discusses the design and implementation of a massive MIMO testbed, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), computer architecture (cs.AR), systems and control (cs.SY), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
